602b4018-2671-11b2-a8a9-43c5b3e1ce97.title: The Exercise 3' Skort
602b4018-2671-11b2-a8a9-43c5b3e1ce97.description: This sporty skort is versatile and confidence boosting. Made in our breathable LightSpeed fabric featuring a built-in shorts liner and phone pocket, now with an updated fit and shorts that stay put.

602b4962-2671-11b2-94a3-9bad688e0159.title: Everyday Boyfriend Tank
602b4962-2671-11b2-94a3-9bad688e0159.description: Boxy but cropped, this 100% cotton tank is a perfect everyday or post-Doing Things layer.

602b5254-2671-11b2-a3f9-f5ba9edeb700.title: TechSweat™ 5' Thrive Short
602b5254-2671-11b2-a3f9-f5ba9edeb700.description: Stays in place while hugging all the right spots. Designed for maximum mobility without weighing you down, this short features our super secure, high-waisted Thrive Band engineered to prevent awkward slips during high-intensity exercise.

602b5a54-2671-11b2-ace4-ab3405de2197.title: Venus Crop Top
602b5a54-2671-11b2-ace4-ab3405de2197.description: A light support V-back crop with signature colorblocking. Made in shape-sculpting Textured Compression for low intensity Recreation.

602b6212-2671-11b2-b6d1-5d30a4c174c6.title: RecNylon 3' Skort
602b6212-2671-11b2-b6d1-5d30a4c174c6.description: Our lightweight short is now a skort. Made from 100% recycled nylon, the RecNylon 3” Skort is high-waisted, wind & water-resistant, and features three total pockets, plus a belted, adjustable waistband.

602b69c4-2671-11b2-b5f1-9f78a37a36ae.title: SoftRib Tank
602b69c4-2671-11b2-b5f1-9f78a37a36ae.description: Lightweight, breathable, and as soft as it is strong. Our SoftRib Tank is an easy-layering basic that wears like it’s barely there — made in our stretchy, shape-hugging fabric known for holding its own against regular wash and wear.

602b71b8-2671-11b2-9ca1-518906b03769.title: FreeForm 3' Skort
602b71b8-2671-11b2-9ca1-518906b03769.description: Looks like a skirt, plays like a short. Ultra-comfortable, with a soft and flattering stretch, the FreeForm 3” Skort features side slits, side pockets, and shorts that stay put.

602b7a22-2671-11b2-9af5-7b45674df91d.title: FreeForm Bra
602b7a22-2671-11b2-9af5-7b45674df91d.description: Perfectly snug and peachy-soft to the touch. Give the ladies a lift in this stretchy-yet-supportive scoop bra, featuring a flattering racerback cut and removable padding.

602b8170-2671-11b2-885c-69af5e2e0518.title: FreeForm 5' Short
602b8170-2671-11b2-885c-69af5e2e0518.description: Your go-to studio shorts, now just a little shorter. Made in our peachy-soft FreeForm fabric, featuring a high-rise fold-over waistband for unrestricted comfort. Product was formerly called Flow 5' Short.

602b88b0-2671-11b2-b1c0-51f8e49f9c8a.title: RecTrek Skirt
602b88b0-2671-11b2-b1c0-51f8e49f9c8a.description: The perfect skirt for all of your adventure needs. Made in our wind and water resistant RecTrek fabric that is flexible, crisp to the touch, and deceivingly lightweight — on or off the trail. Designed for layering.

602b9024-2671-11b2-8c26-eb3f95e0f1f5.title: RecTrek Relaxed Pant
602b9024-2671-11b2-8c26-eb3f95e0f1f5.description: Our most versatile pant for outdoor recreation. Made in durable, elements-resistant RecTrek, featuring a generous, wide-leg fit for extra mobility and comfort.

602b97b2-2671-11b2-9469-f9e09c3bcbdb.title: SolarCool 6' Beach Boardshort
602b97b2-2671-11b2-9469-f9e09c3bcbdb.description: An unlined, quick-drying short for sun, water, and sweat. Built with serious UPF 50+ sun protection, an adjustable waistband, and plenty of pockets.

602b9fba-2671-11b2-838a-e1507828defd.title: Organic Cotton Terry Crewneck Sweatshirt
602b9fba-2671-11b2-838a-e1507828defd.description: Toss on and go. A relaxed crewneck in lightweight and plush Organic Cotton Terry fabric you'll never want to take off.

602ba9d0-2671-11b2-a1ac-0fae29edf12b.title: High Stride 7' Short with Pockets - Unlined
602ba9d0-2671-11b2-a1ac-0fae29edf12b.description: An unlined short for running and training, now featuring identical right and left pockets. Made in lightweight, sweat-wicking Train Stretch Woven, featuring GridTek paneling for increased mobility and internal drawstrings for adjustability.

602bb930-2671-11b2-a9d1-85226f551eac.title: High Stride 5' Short with Pockets - Unlined
602bb930-2671-11b2-a9d1-85226f551eac.description: An unlined short for running and training, now featuring identical right and left pockets. Made in lightweight, sweat-wicking Train Stretch Woven, featuring GridTek paneling for increased mobility and internal drawstrings for adjustability.

602bc067-2671-11b2-8c96-85eba5bb4b32.title: Take A Lap Graphic Everyday Longsleeve
602bc067-2671-11b2-8c96-85eba5bb4b32.description: Chase endorphins daily in our unisex Everyday Longsleeve. Made in 100% Organic Cotton Jersey with graphic detail on both the front and back.

602bc76a-2671-11b2-a044-979b3e9e22b6.title: Earthing Unisex Graphic Pickup Sweatshirt
602bc76a-2671-11b2-a044-979b3e9e22b6.description: Stay grounded, get moving. Made in our plush Organic Cotton Terry fabric, this oversized crewneck sweatshirt features a roomy, unisex fit and graphic detail.

602bcf40-2671-11b2-b7ae-11cfa5ef8d98.title: RecTrek Zip-Up
602bcf40-2671-11b2-b7ae-11cfa5ef8d98.description: The RecTrek Zip Up is a durable, water-resistant outer layer for Doing Things outdoors, featuring a packable windbreaker hood, ample storage space, back ventilation, and a bungee hem for a customized fit.

602bd6e7-2671-11b2-999c-c7e55867003a.title: Technical Apparel Unisex Pickup Hoodie
602bd6e7-2671-11b2-999c-c7e55867003a.description: Everyday comfort has entered the chat. Move freely from your warm-up to your cooldown in this classic oversized hoodie. Made in plush Organic Cotton Terry with our “Technical Apparel” tote graphic.

602bdd03-2671-11b2-ac2e-03c3912710b8.title: Team OV Unisex Graphic Pickup Hoodie
602bdd03-2671-11b2-ac2e-03c3912710b8.description: High five — you’re on the team. Made in our plush Organic Cotton Terry fabric, this classic unisex hoodie is a natural fit for getting outside (and/or hinting that’s where you’d rather be).

602be235-2671-11b2-8741-210fac7adc09.title: Nimbus Classic Sweatshirt
602be235-2671-11b2-8741-210fac7adc09.description: A classic crewneck sweatshirt made in our heavyweight Nimbus Cotton. Featuring a comfortable, unisex fit, a fleecy-soft inside, and raglan-style sleeves.

602be7b3-2671-11b2-8b3f-45e28c3bdd8e.title: Doing Good Things Graphic Shortsleeve
602be7b3-2671-11b2-8b3f-45e28c3bdd8e.description: Together with the YMCA, we’re Doing Good Things. Made in our Organic Cotton Terry and produced in the US, this unisex tee features a limited-edition graphic. 100% of the profits from this sweatshirt will go towards the YMCA.

eb30051e-2690-11b2-b312-71994192e095.title: Love it!
eb30051e-2690-11b2-b312-71994192e095.body: I love this skirt! It is perfect to go play tennis in! It fits so great and is so fun to wear! The material is great quality and I highly recommend this product
eb30051e-2690-11b2-b312-71994192e095.name: Lauren

eb303a22-2690-11b2-ab86-83a74e8a7c58.title: Love
eb303a22-2690-11b2-ab86-83a74e8a7c58.body: So so comfy. Love this top for everyday fits and walks! Will definitely be buying in more colors!
eb303a22-2690-11b2-ab86-83a74e8a7c58.name: Isabelle

eb2fc098-2690-11b2-90b6-b58a520132ce.title: Supper flattering!!
eb2fc098-2690-11b2-90b6-b58a520132ce.body: Love the built in bra for a little extra support and the material is great for if you're gonna work up a little sweat as well. It's just a touch long on me (I'm 5' 4") but the seams on the side and the super light flare at the bottom of the dress make it so, so flattering.
eb2fc098-2690-11b2-90b6-b58a520132ce.name: Sydne

eb3066db-2690-11b2-8dbb-9deac4ce569e.title: Great shorts
eb3066db-2690-11b2-8dbb-9deac4ce569e.body: I really like the fabric of these shorts. It’s both cooling and compressive. The silicone on the edge of the shorts is AMAZING and I wish it came on all biker shorts. The cut is flattering, and cameltoe free. I also like the slightly longer length because it protects against thigh chafe! Liked them so much I bought a second color. I wear these to run or walk in. I am 5’5 and 150 lbs -athletic build (aka I’ve got big legs lol) and I got a medium.
eb3066db-2690-11b2-8dbb-9deac4ce569e.name: Jo

eb3250bd-2690-11b2-b464-43bc84df95be.title: Great for running!
eb3250bd-2690-11b2-b464-43bc84df95be.body: I loveeeee these. The waistband stays up nicely on runs. The band does give me a littleeee bit of tummy bulge, but I don't mind. That's just my body. They take a bit of effort to pull up over thicker thighs, but once on, they feel great and are very comfortable to me. I'm a 28/29 in pants with larger hips and the small worked well for me.
eb3250bd-2690-11b2-b464-43bc84df95be.name: Mary

eb305fd5-2690-11b2-ac41-2f9243434c38.title: My favorite top! I even wear it out!
eb305fd5-2690-11b2-ac41-2f9243434c38.body: This is such a versatile top! I wear it to work out in but every once in a while I wear it when I go out with friends and I always get compliments on it! Super flattering too and not see through at all
eb305fd5-2690-11b2-ac41-2f9243434c38.name: Elle

eb3085c7-2690-11b2-8ba7-6f2335eb9478.title: 4.5 stars- Almost perfect
eb3085c7-2690-11b2-8ba7-6f2335eb9478.body: The adjustable belt is sewn in which means you can’t actually adjust it like you with the zip offs. I wish there was a side zipper because it is difficult to get the skirt over your hips if you have a butt. I would not size up personally since the waist can’t be adjusted that much. Once it’s on, however it is so cute. The Laurel Wreath color is the perfect cargo shorts for people w/cool skin tones. However, I hope they adjust the design in the future because it is almost perfect hence the 4.5.
eb3085c7-2690-11b2-8ba7-6f2335eb9478.name: Sara

eb2febab-2690-11b2-8148-8b50d66b87ad.title: Cute Dress, Great Gift!
eb2febab-2690-11b2-8148-8b50d66b87ad.body: I ordered this dress as a gift for my brother's girlfriend, and she absolutely adores it! I own two colors myself, and think the dress really hugs the right places and provides support where needed. It was great to see that this dress is so versatile for activities and body types!
eb2febab-2690-11b2-8148-8b50d66b87ad.name: Hannah

eb3205f8-2690-11b2-8baa-1b25c621f749.title: Best fitting basic ever
eb3205f8-2690-11b2-8baa-1b25c621f749.body: Obsessed with this top! The fit is perfect for an everyday basic and feels so good! Washes up and doesn’t get dingey white at all!
eb3205f8-2690-11b2-8baa-1b25c621f749.name: Mia

eb308c15-2690-11b2-a3c0-751fe3f96102.title: i NEED more!
eb308c15-2690-11b2-a3c0-751fe3f96102.body: This top is great for everyday and is adorable! It works best with a thin, cross-strap bra or none at all, depending on your preference. I loved the cappuccino color and hope to see more of these in the future!
eb308c15-2690-11b2-a3c0-751fe3f96102.name: Hannah

eb30af94-2690-11b2-bb9b-cd3786f4b53e.title: Love love love
eb30af94-2690-11b2-bb9b-cd3786f4b53e.body: I really love this skort! The fabric feels like butter. I took my regular size but I do wish it was just a tad longer. Very cute set!
eb30af94-2690-11b2-bb9b-cd3786f4b53e.name: Natalie

eb30cded-2690-11b2-a1bf-e790aa1c4bc6.title: Comfortable and flattering
eb30cded-2690-11b2-a1bf-e790aa1c4bc6.body: I bought this to go with the skirt and it does not disappoint. Very versatile bra. Can be worn for anything. I recommend. Fabric is also very soft.
eb30cded-2690-11b2-a1bf-e790aa1c4bc6.name: Abi

eb2fd2c6-2690-11b2-b56d-f9ed334eb09b.title: Perfect Summer Short
eb2fd2c6-2690-11b2-b56d-f9ed334eb09b.body: I bought these for an upcoming beach vacation and cannot wait to wear them! The high waist is super flattering and the length is just right for my heigh (5’5”). Plus the fabric will be perfect for the warm temps.
eb2fd2c6-2690-11b2-b56d-f9ed334eb09b.name: Katelyn

eb310855-2690-11b2-8734-37be1d4f7e3d.title: Soft and comfy for this pregnant lady
eb310855-2690-11b2-8734-37be1d4f7e3d.body: I purchased the Free Form 5" in black and also the Warmup Short - I returned the Warmups and kept these because the material and fit were way better for my preferences (lounging and also wearing for spin class/weightlifting). The compression is less intense than the Warmups and therefore fit me better, even when 4 months pregnant. After receiving the black I wanted to purchase more colors but they are all sold out in my size which is a shame. I sized up due to being pregnant but fit seems right.
eb310855-2690-11b2-8734-37be1d4f7e3d.name: AB

eb2ffc39-2690-11b2-844e-c52e4e8ad350.title: Really great. Wearing right now
eb2ffc39-2690-11b2-844e-c52e4e8ad350.body: I’ve been wearing these a ton since I got them. They run slightly large on me. I’m a typical medium (5’9”, 140 lb) and the leg opening on the medium is almost too wide/flared. I got them in black and would get in the blue if they had them in stock. Love the large pockets
eb2ffc39-2690-11b2-844e-c52e4e8ad350.name: Lauren

eb317300-2690-11b2-a776-af09ad9b4d5c.title: Great skirt
eb317300-2690-11b2-a776-af09ad9b4d5c.body: I have the reck treck pants and shorts as well. Normally a small in OV pants/shorts, have a found a medium in OV skirts/skorts fit better (5’2”, 113lbs).
eb317300-2690-11b2-a776-af09ad9b4d5c.name: Sara

eb304026-2690-11b2-9ae6-73209b15adf5.title: These are the comfiest leggings ever
eb304026-2690-11b2-9ae6-73209b15adf5.body: I absolutely love these. Prefect thickness, love the texture. Love the subtle design. Love the color. Did I say I love these? Highly recommend!!! I got a medium. 30.5” waist; 42.5” hip; 170lbs Definitely not 7/8 length like Lululemon, but I’d pick these over lulus always.
eb304026-2690-11b2-9ae6-73209b15adf5.name: Bronson

eb32b6ec-2690-11b2-80b8-176ed5e0ebcb.title: Love the fit!
eb32b6ec-2690-11b2-80b8-176ed5e0ebcb.body: I'm 107lbs, small chested (32b) and in the pic I'm wearing xxs - love how it's a little tight around the forearms but not the upper arms/shoulders! It's the right type of loose and the material is so soft! Love love love!
eb32b6ec-2690-11b2-80b8-176ed5e0ebcb.name: Julieanne

eb2fc718-2690-11b2-90f5-3719435cc9d3.title: Versatile!
eb2fc718-2690-11b2-90f5-3719435cc9d3.body: I love the matieral of this skirt and the length! I have an outdoors job and it’s perfect for that! I found my normal size, M, to be a bit large in the waist. But the S was too tight across my hips so I went with the medium. So comfortable and cute!
eb2fc718-2690-11b2-90f5-3719435cc9d3.name: Sarah

eb335d9d-2690-11b2-a782-fba9041d12cf.title: Amazing, cozy, must have!!
eb335d9d-2690-11b2-a782-fba9041d12cf.body: I've been searching for the perfect, cozy pullover for the chillier months. This was PERFECT. It's much thicker and softer than the terry cotton crew neck, and also a much more relaxed fit. Ideal for workout pullover, yoga, pilates, or walks. I wanted something super oversized and slouchy, so I actually sized up quite a bit. But it's a must have, high recommend!
eb335d9d-2690-11b2-a782-fba9041d12cf.name: Ali

eb31edad-2690-11b2-a7c8-b52aa9740c20.title: Cute and warm
eb31edad-2690-11b2-a7c8-b52aa9740c20.body: Bought for skiing and can't wait to wear next winter!
eb31edad-2690-11b2-a7c8-b52aa9740c20.name: Kiki

eb3010ab-2690-11b2-9e15-b33d38ad77d6.title: Adorable!!
eb3010ab-2690-11b2-9e15-b33d38ad77d6.body: This top is perfect for running, it fits well and is very comfortable. It’s also so cute!! 10/10 would buy in a￼ different color.
eb3010ab-2690-11b2-9e15-b33d38ad77d6.name: Anne

eb318cf1-2690-11b2-b5ec-1fe067b5d0e8.title: Love!
eb318cf1-2690-11b2-b5ec-1fe067b5d0e8.body: Love this hoodie and I wish the shorts were in stock so I could get it as a set. Material is light and comfy. True to size, please make in more colors!
eb318cf1-2690-11b2-b5ec-1fe067b5d0e8.name: Grace

eb33b5d5-2690-11b2-a512-5faa7e99d024.title: PHENOMENAL JACKET
eb33b5d5-2690-11b2-a512-5faa7e99d024.body: A breathable rainy day jacket, I bought a large so I could layer underneath as well! Used it in the winter snow! it kept me adequately warm and dry, the only down side was I didn’t realize I got snow in my pocket and went indoors and it melted. I didn’t know it was there until I reached into my pocket and there was a puddle of water. I learned to button it for next time. I love this jacket so much. Glad I made the investment it’s a great quality!
eb33b5d5-2690-11b2-a512-5faa7e99d024.name: Nayelly

eb33a28b-2690-11b2-bb0f-83a206776a9a.title: Softest
eb33a28b-2690-11b2-bb0f-83a206776a9a.body: Great sweats, the soft texture never fades
eb33a28b-2690-11b2-bb0f-83a206776a9a.name: Nadia

eb339596-2690-11b2-9906-cd87f5da47d4.title: Best sweats
eb339596-2690-11b2-9906-cd87f5da47d4.body: I accidentally bought these in the wrong size and since they no longer have them in stock I gave them to my sister. It’s her second pair and she loves them! Please please bring these back in all the colors so that I can get another pair!
eb339596-2690-11b2-9906-cd87f5da47d4.name: Becky

eb32c79b-2690-11b2-a545-6d4c1082e293.title: Perfect sweatshirt
eb32c79b-2690-11b2-a545-6d4c1082e293.body: I am a sweatshirt SNOB - this is my favorite sweatshirt I’ve ever owned. So soft, stretchy in all the best ways, super easy to throw on.
eb32c79b-2690-11b2-a545-6d4c1082e293.name: Brett

eb336c67-2690-11b2-823e-1557646b6571.title: favorite t-shirt
eb336c67-2690-11b2-823e-1557646b6571.body: I bought an extra size or two up so it would be a baggy fit on me. One of the most comfortable tshirts I've ever owned and it's so cute! It's my go to fave.
eb336c67-2690-11b2-823e-1557646b6571.name: Koty
